meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , ROUND_DAY ( "EKBE"."BUDAT" ) , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' ) < ROUND_DAY ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) AND 2 = 1 THEN 'affected' WHEN PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , ROUND_DAY ( "EKBE"."BUDAT" ) , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' ) < ROUND_DAY ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) AND 2 = 2 THEN 'affected' WHEN 2 = 3 AND PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , ROUND_DAY ( "EKBE"."BUDAT" ) , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '1' ) < ROUND_DAY ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) OR 2 = 3 AND PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , ROUND_DAY ( "EKBE"."BUDAT" ) , "EKBE"."VGABE" = '2' ) < ROUND_DAY ( "EKKO"."AEDAT" ) THEN 'affected' ELSE 'not affected' END AS "Indicator"
